work.work-title: Thou Shepherd of Israel, and mine

credit.credit-words: Ah! show me that happiest place, That place of Thy people's abode; Where saints in an ecstasy gaze, And hang on a crucified God: Thy love for a sinner declare, Thy passion and death on the tree; My spirit to Calvary bear, To suffer, and triumph with Thee.
Thou Shepherd of Israel, and mine
